{
  "stem": "26142.15",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Number 15 with Michael Jackson.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was talking about his cousin who was mistreated by the Russians.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was captured by the Russian with-- with other Hungarian Jewish labor units.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were mistreated.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he died already.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And never-- he never came home.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] We are talking now-- we are in-- in May 1944.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- I was telling that we thought that we-- we were surrendered.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Of course, the [NON-ENGLISH] the [NON-ENGLISH] is called the fence.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "This-- the-- the soldiers, the Hungarian soldiers that were watching us in Hungary, they are called the [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were 14, 15 soldiers, a sergeant, and the commander.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The commander was usually an officer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It could be a captain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Or it could be a major or it could be lieutenant.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] They were surrendered-- surrounded.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we-- we saw-- we saw somebody-- very-- very pleasant things, we could-- I should say, we saw.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The Germans were mostly mechanized more than the Hungarian army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "The Hungarians had horses and wagons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they-- they had-- they were having truck.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "The had also-- the Hungarians also had trucks, but not as many as the Germans.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And when they were moving back, the Germans were running so bad, that they-- they-- they choked up the-- the highways.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So they were even throwing the Hungarians off the highways in order so that-- that-- they could pass through there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So there was-- we saw a conflict between the two-- between the two.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the Hungarians-- of course, the Hungarians don't understand German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And the German don't understand Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They were cursing at each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But we-- we-- we understood both languages.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "But somehow or other, we got-- we got through there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "They broke-- the-- the Germans broke out.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
